scripts.postinstall: node -e "try { const tf = require('@tensorflow/tfjs-node'); if (tf.node && tf.node.decodeImage) { console.log('✅ TensorFlow.js Node backend available'); } else { throw new Error('Stub detected'); } } catch(e) { console.log('⚠️  Creating TensorFlow.js Node compatibility stub...'); const fs = require('fs'); const path = require('path'); const dir = path.join('node_modules', '@tensorflow'); if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) fs.mkdirSync(dir, {recursive: true}); fs.writeFileSync(path.join(dir, 'tfjs-node.js'), 'module.exports = require(\"@tensorflow/tfjs\");'); console.log('✅ Compatibility stub created'); }"
